c: 4
v: 20
t: "Futhi uma nifisa ukuthatha omunye unkosikazi esikhundleni somunye unkosikazi nibe nanika oyedwa wabo (abesifazane) isipho esikhulu (somshado) nize ningabothatha lutho kusona nilubuyisele emumva ngisho nakancane ngakube nisithatha ngendlela\tengafanele\tnengenabo\tubulungiswa\t(lokho) kuyisono esisobala"